    • Field Detail

      • restaurantid

        private long restaurantid
        The primary key number (long) of the restaurants table.

      • name

        private java.lang.String name
        The name (String) of the restaurant. Cannot be null and must be unique.

      • address

        private java.lang.String address
        The address (String) of the restaurant. Any format is acceptable.

      • city

        private java.lang.String city
        The city (String) of the restaurant. Any format is acceptable.

      • state

        private java.lang.String state
        The state (String) of the restaurant. The format is the two character abbreviation of the state.

      • telephone

        private java.lang.String telephone
        The telephone number (String) of the restaurant. Any format is acceptable.

      • hasvalueforseatcapacity

        public boolean hasvalueforseatcapacity
        Used to determine if the field seatcapacity has been set or is NULL, meaning 0 for an integer value. Does not get saved to the database.

      • seatcapacity

        private int seatcapacity
        The seating capacity (integer) of the restaurant. This was added to specifically show how to update fields that do not have a NULL value.

      • payments

        java.util.List<Payment> payments
        Creates a join table joining Restaurants and Payments in a Many-To-Many relations. Contains a List of Payment Objects used by this restaurant.

      • menus

        private java.util.List<Menu> menus
        List of menus associated with this restaurant. Does not get saved in the database directly. Forms a One-To-Many relationship to menus. One restaurant to many menus.

      • setSeatcapacity

        public void setSeatcapacity​(int seatcapacity)
        Setter for seatcapacity.

        If the value is set through the JPA, specifically through a JSON object set to this API, hasvaluefor will be set to true. Otherwise it defaults to false. This allows the application to tell if a seatcapacity is 0 because it was set as 0 or because it is not set and thus should be considered NULL but is in fact 0.

        Parameters:
        seatcapacity - The new amount (integer) of seats this restaurant has.
